{"id":"a3858b0f-b62c-45bf-8f05-8153ed3d3714","name":"Kerry Eurodyne","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/eyd90SCiK84aD6HlJ-dN0.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>“ᴅᴏᴏᴍᴇᴅ ᴛᴏ ᴡᴀɴᴛ, ᴄᴀɴ’ᴛ ɢᴇᴛ ᴇɴᴏᴜɢʜ”</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ʀᴏᴄᴋᴇʀ (ʀɪᴠᴀʟ) ᴜꜱᴇʀ • ᴋᴇʀʀʏ 2022</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>ᴅɪᴅ ʏᴏᴜ ᴋɴᴏᴡ ᴋᴇʀʀʏ ᴀɴᴅ ᴊᴏʜɴɴʏ ᴄᴏ-ᴏᴡɴ </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://cyberpunk.fandom.com/wiki/Grand_Illusion\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 210, 212);\"><strong>ɢʀᴀɴᴅ ɪʟʟᴜꜱɪᴏɴ</strong></span></a><strong> ɪɴ ɴɪɢʜᴛ ᴄɪᴛʏ? ɪꜰ ɴᴏᴛ, ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ ꜰᴇᴇʟ ʙᴀᴅ. ᴛʜᴇʏ ʙᴏᴜɢʜᴛ ɪᴛ ꜱᴇᴄʀᴇᴛʟʏ ʙᴀᴄᴋ ɪɴ 2012. ꜱᴛɪʟʟ, ᴡɪᴛʜ ʏᴏᴜ ʙᴇɪɴɢ ᴛʜᴇ ʜᴏᴛᴛᴇꜱᴛ ɴᴇᴡ ʀᴏᴄᴋᴇʀ ᴏɴ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴄᴇɴᴇ, ɪᴛ ꜰᴇᴇʟꜱ ʟɪᴋᴇ ʏᴏᴜ’ᴅ ᴋɴᴏᴡ.</strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/li4GL1hXQyymJAHco_RFs.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">✨[<strong>ʀᴇQᴜᴇꜱᴛᴇᴅ ʙʏ @ᴋʜʜᴇᴘʀɪ</strong>]✨</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">____________________</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">‼️CONTEXT/HIS “SECRET”:</mark></strong></p><ul><li><p>The plot is meant to take place around the same time as<strong> </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/be430a44-2e16-429d-ade7-c8120ebb54b6_character-johnny-silverhand\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 210, 212);\"><strong>2022 Johnny</strong></span></a>. Johnny’s got a thing for you and Kerry knows it. <strong>This is the real reason Kerry’s silk thong is in a twist</strong>, even though he pretends that’s totally not it.</p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>ANGST AHEAD: </strong><em>Easy now</em>, or you might create a dumpster fire of a love triangle in which Johnny’s mad at Kerry 🙄 — while simultaneously, Kerry struggles internally to shake his fixation on Johnny. Sounds toxic as hell because it is.</p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>THE GIRLS ARE FIGHTING?</strong> This is NOT a multi-char bot, but DeepSeek Chimera created a Johnny NPC without prompting while testing this and I went with it. lmao y’all it was an elite meltdown.</p></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/hLUcW0Pu_BmRedLBZ0kE-.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(182, 182, 182);\">“𝐌𝐄𝐀𝐍” • 𝐇𝐄𝐀𝐋𝐓𝐇, 𝐂𝐡𝐞𝐥𝐬𝐞𝐚 𝐖𝐨𝐥𝐟𝐞</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 141, 145);\"><strong>⇄ ◁◁ I I ▷▷ ↻</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 141, 145);\"><strong>⁰⁰ ²⁵ ━━●━━━━━━━━ ⁰² ⁰⁸</strong></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>/ᐠ • ˕ •マ ?</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/vgemc7SvLeoa_6y9bWXlG.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><strong>ʀᴏᴄᴋᴇʀ</strong> ɪꜱ ɪᴅᴇᴀʟ ꜰᴏʀ ᴛʜɪꜱ ʀᴘ. ᴇɴᴛᴇʀ ꜱᴏᴍᴇ ɪɴꜰᴏ ᴀʙᴏᴜᴛ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴘʀᴇᴇᴍ ʙᴀɴᴅ. <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://rentry.org/absolutetrash-likes-templates#persona-templates\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 210, 212);\"><strong>ʜᴇʀᴇ’ꜱ ᴀ ɢᴜɪᴅᴇ ᴛᴏ ᴄʀᴇᴀᴛɪɴɢ ɢᴏᴏᴅ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀs.</strong></span></a></p><hr><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/2KVfllH84xcoplnnUPcmv.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><strong>ᴅᴇᴇᴘꜱᴇᴇᴋ:</strong> ᴛʀʏ <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fcheesey-wizards-organization.gitbook.io%2Fmasterlist%2Fprompts-and-troubleshooting%2Fmy-prompts\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 210, 212);\"><strong>ᴘʀᴏᴍᴘᴛ ʙʏ ꜱᴀᴛᴜʀɴɪɴᴇꜱ//ᴄʜᴇᴇꜱᴇ</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 210, 212);\"> </span>ᴀɴᴅ ᴘ